✅ Confirmation candle must CLOSE — never enter on open candle
✅ Wick-to-body ratio for Pin Bar: wick ≥ 2× body length
✅ Engulfing: body of signal candle must fully engulf prior candle body
✅ Volume on signal candle should be ≥ average (stronger signal)
❌ Patterns in the middle of a range = lower reliability → mark as Tier 3

