SCALING-IN FRAMEWORK (Split Risk)

Total Risk per Trade: $30 (1% of capital)

Entry Strategy Options:

OPTION A — Standard (Single Entry)
• 100% position at Entry 1
• Use when: Setup is ⭐⭐⭐ high confidence, tight SL available

OPTION B — Scaled Entry (2-Part)
• 60% position at Entry 1 (primary trigger level)
• 40% position at Entry 2 (deeper zone: next OB/FVG or fractal level)
• SL for both = below/above the deepest entry zone
• Use when: Setup is ⭐⭐ medium confidence, wider SL zone

OPTION C — Pyramid (Add on Confirmation)
• 70% position at Entry 1
• 30% added ONLY after BOS in trade direction confirms momentum
• SL moved to breakeven on Entry 1 before adding
• Use when: Breakout setup or momentum-based entry

