−0.5 ⭐ : < 3/5 macro-correlated assets support trade direction
−1.0 ⭐ : Pattern contradicts higher-TF trend (counter-trend setup)
−1.0 ⭐ : OI falling while trading in move direction (unwinding)

If calculated R:R < MIN R:R → override bias to ⚪ WAIT

